{"thag19.1:0.1":"Theragatha 19.1 ","thag19.1:0.2":"Pannasanipata ","thag19.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag19.1:0.4":"Talaputattheragatha ","thag19.1:1.1":"“Kada nuham pabbatakandarasu, ","thag19.1:1.2":"Ekakiyo addutiyo vihassam; ","thag19.1:1.3":"Aniccato sabbabhavam vipassam, ","thag19.1:1.4":"Tam me idam tam nu kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:2.1":"Kada nuham bhinnapatandharo muni, ","thag19.1:2.2":"Kasavavattho amamo niraso; ","thag19.1:2.3":"Raganca dosanca tatheva moham, ","thag19.1:2.4":"Hantva sukhi pavanagato vihassam. ","thag19.1:3.1":"Kada aniccam vadharoganilam, ","thag19.1:3.2":"Kayam imam maccujarayupaddutam; ","thag19.1:3.3":"Vipassamano vitabhayo vihassam, ","thag19.1:3.4":"Eko vane tam nu kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:4.1":"Kada nuham bhayajananim dukhavaham, ","thag19.1:4.2":"Tanhalatam bahuvidhanuvattanim; ","thag19.1:4.3":"Pannamayam tikhinamasim gahetva, ","thag19.1:4.4":"Chetva vase tampi kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:5.1":"Kada nu pannamayamuggatejam, ","thag19.1:5.2":"Sattham isinam sahasadiyitva; ","thag19.1:5.3":"Maram sasenam sahasa bhanjissam, ","thag19.1:5.4":"Sihasane tam nu kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:6.1":"Kada nuham sabbhi samagamesu, ","thag19.1:6.2":"Dittho bhave dhammagaruhi tadibhi; ","thag19.1:6.3":"Yathavadassihi jitindriyehi, ","thag19.1:6.4":"Padhaniyo tam nu kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:7.1":"Kada nu mam tandi khuda pipasa, ","thag19.1:7.2":"Vatatapa kitasarisapa va; ","thag19.1:7.3":"Na badhayissanti na tam giribbaje, ","thag19.1:7.4":"Atthatthiyam tam nu kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:8.1":"Kada nu kho yam viditam mahesina, ","thag19.1:8.2":"Cattari saccani sududdasani; ","thag19.1:8.3":"Samahitatto satima agaccham, ","thag19.1:8.4":"Pannaya tam tam nu kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:9.1":"Kada nu rupe amite ca sadde, ","thag19.1:9.2":"Gandhe rase phusitabbe ca dhamme; ","thag19.1:9.3":"Adittatoham samathehi yutto, ","thag19.1:9.4":"Pannaya daccham tadidam kada me. ","thag19.1:10.1":"Kada nuham dubbacanena vutto, ","thag19.1:10.2":"Tato nimittam vimano na hessam; ","thag19.1:10.3":"Atho pasatthopi tato nimittam, ","thag19.1:10.4":"Tuttho na hessam tadidam kada me. ","thag19.1:11.1":"Kada nu katthe ca tine lata ca, ","thag19.1:11.2":"Khandhe imeham amite ca dhamme; ","thag19.1:11.3":"Ajjhattikaneva ca bahirani ca, ","thag19.1:11.4":"Samam tuleyyam tadidam kada me. ","thag19.1:12.1":"Kada nu mam pavusakalamegho, ","thag19.1:12.2":"Navena toyena sacivaram vane; ","thag19.1:12.3":"Isippayatamhi pathe vajantam, ","thag19.1:12.4":"Ovassate tam nu kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:13.1":"Kada mayurassa sikhandino vane, ","thag19.1:13.2":"Dijassa sutva girigabbhare rutam; ","thag19.1:13.3":"Paccutthahitva amatassa pattiya, ","thag19.1:13.4":"Sancintaye tam nu kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:14.1":"Kada nu gangam yamunam sarassatim, ","thag19.1:14.2":"Patalakhittam valavamukhanca; ","thag19.1:14.3":"Asajjamano patareyyamiddhiya, ","thag19.1:14.4":"Vibhimsanam tam nu kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:15.1":"Kada nu nagova asangacari, ","thag19.1:15.2":"Padalaye kamagunesu chandam; ","thag19.1:15.3":"Nibbajjayam sabbasubham nimittam, ","thag19.1:15.4":"Jhane yuto tam nu kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:16.1":"Kada inattova daliddako nidhim, ","thag19.1:16.2":"Aradhayitva dhanikehi pilito; ","thag19.1:16.3":"Tuttho bhavissam adhigamma sasanam, ","thag19.1:16.4":"Mahesino tam nu kada bhavissati. ","thag19.1:17.1":"Bahuni vassani tayamhi yacito, ","thag19.1:17.2":"‘Agaravasena alam nu te idam’; ","thag19.1:17.3":"Tam dani mam pabbajitam samanam, ","thag19.1:17.4":"Kinkarana citta tuvam na yunjasi. ","thag19.1:18.1":"Nanu aham citta tayamhi yacito, ","thag19.1:18.2":"‘Giribbaje citrachada vihangama’; ","thag19.1:18.3":"Mahindaghosatthanitabhigajjino, ","thag19.1:18.4":"Te tam ramessanti vanamhi jhayinam. ","thag19.1:19.1":"Kulamhi mitte ca piye ca natake, ","thag19.1:19.2":"Khiddaratim kamagunanca loke; ","thag19.1:19.3":"Sabbam pahaya imamajjhupagato, ","thag19.1:19.4":"Athopi tvam citta na mayha tussasi. ","thag19.1:20.1":"Mameva etam na hi tvam paresam, ","thag19.1:20.2":"Sannahakale paridevitena kim; ","thag19.1:20.3":"Sabbam idam calamiti pekkhamano, ","thag19.1:20.4":"Abhinikkhamim amatapadam jigisam. ","thag19.1:21.1":"Suyuttavadi dvipadanamuttamo, ","thag19.1:21.2":"Mahabhisakko naradammasarathi; ","thag19.1:21.3":"‘Cittam calam makkatasannibham iti, ","thag19.1:21.4":"Avitaragena sudunnivarayam’. ","thag19.1:22.1":"Kama hi citra madhura manorama, ","thag19.1:22.2":"Aviddasu yattha sita puthujjana; ","thag19.1:22.3":"Te dukkhamicchanti punabbhavesino, ","thag19.1:22.4":"Cittena nita niraye nirakata. ","thag19.1:23.1":"‘Mayurakoncabhirutamhi kanane, ","thag19.1:23.2":"Dipihi byagghehi purakkhato vasam; ","thag19.1:23.3":"Kaye apekkham jaha ma viradhaya’, ","thag19.1:23.4":"Itissu mam citta pure niyunjasi. ","thag19.1:24.1":"‘Bhavehi jhanani ca indriyani ca, ","thag19.1:24.2":"Balani bojjhangasamadhibhavana; ","thag19.1:24.3":"Tisso ca vijja phusa buddhasasane’, ","thag19.1:24.4":"Itissu mam citta pure niyunjasi. ","thag19.1:25.1":"‘Bhavehi maggam amatassa pattiya, ","thag19.1:25.2":"Niyyanikam sabbadukhakkhayogadham; ","thag19.1:25.3":"Atthangikam sabbakilesasodhanam’, ","thag19.1:25.4":"Itissu mam citta pure niyunjasi. ","thag19.1:26.1":"‘Dukkhanti khandhe patipassa yoniso, ","thag19.1:26.2":"Yato ca dukkham samudeti tam jaha; ","thag19.1:26.3":"Idheva dukkhassa karohi antam’, ","thag19.1:26.4":"Itissu mam citta pure niyunjasi. ","thag19.1:27.1":"‘Aniccam dukkhanti vipassa yoniso, ","thag19.1:27.2":"Sunnam anattati agham vadhanti ca; ","thag19.1:27.3":"Manovicare uparundha cetaso’, ","thag19.1:27.4":"Itissu mam citta pure niyunjasi. ","thag19.1:28.1":"‘Mundo virupo abhisapamagato, ","thag19.1:28.2":"Kapalahatthova kulesu bhikkhasu; ","thag19.1:28.3":"Yunjassu satthuvacane mahesino’, ","thag19.1:28.4":"Itissu mam citta pure niyunjasi. ","thag19.1:29.1":"‘Susamvutatto visikhantare caram, ","thag19.1:29.2":"Kulesu kamesu asangamanaso; ","thag19.1:29.3":"Cando yatha dosinapunnamasiya’, ","thag19.1:29.4":"Itissu mam citta pure niyunjasi. ","thag19.1:30.1":"‘Aranniko hohi ca pindapatiko, ","thag19.1:30.2":"Sosaniko hohi ca pamsukuliko; ","thag19.1:30.3":"Nesajjiko hohi sada dhute rato’, ","thag19.1:30.4":"Itissu mam citta pure niyunjasi. ","thag19.1:31.1":"Ropetva rukkhani yatha phalesi, ","thag19.1:31.2":"Mule tarum chettu tameva icchasi; ","thag19.1:31.3":"Tathupamam cittamidam karosi, ","thag19.1:31.4":"Yam mam aniccamhi cale niyunjasi. ","thag19.1:32.1":"Arupa durangama ekacari, ","thag19.1:32.2":"Na te karissam vacanam idaniham; ","thag19.1:32.3":"Dukkha hi kama katuka mahabbhaya, ","thag19.1:32.4":"Nibbanamevabhimano carissam. ","thag19.1:33.1":"Naham alakkhya ahirikkataya va, ","thag19.1:33.2":"Na cittahetu na ca durakantana; ","thag19.1:33.3":"Ajivahetu ca aham na nikkhamim, ","thag19.1:33.4":"Kato ca te citta patissavo maya. ","thag19.1:34.1":"‘Appicchata sappurisehi vannita, ","thag19.1:34.2":"Makkhappahanam vupasamo dukhassa’; ","thag19.1:34.3":"Itissu mam citta tada niyunjasi, ","thag19.1:34.4":"Idani tvam gacchasi pubbacinnam. ","thag19.1:35.1":"Tanha avijja ca piyapiyanca, ","thag19.1:35.2":"Subhani rupani sukha ca vedana; ","thag19.1:35.3":"Manapiya kamaguna ca vanta, ","thag19.1:35.4":"Vante aham avamitum na ussahe. ","thag19.1:36.1":"Sabbattha te citta vaco katam maya, ","thag19.1:36.2":"Bahusu jatisu na mesi kopito; ","thag19.1:36.3":"Ajjhattasambhavo katannutaya te, ","thag19.1:36.4":"Dukkhe ciram samsaritam taya kate. ","thag19.1:37.1":"Tvanneva no citta karosi brahmano, ","thag19.1:37.2":"Tvam khattiyo rajadasi karosi; ","thag19.1:37.3":"Vessa ca sudda ca bhavama ekada, ","thag19.1:37.4":"Devattanam vapi taveva vahasa. ","thag19.1:38.1":"Taveva hetu asura bhavamase, ","thag19.1:38.2":"Tvammulakam nerayika bhavamase; ","thag19.1:38.3":"Atho tiracchanagatapi ekada, ","thag19.1:38.4":"Petattanam vapi taveva vahasa. ","thag19.1:39.1":"Nanu dubbhissasi mam punappunam, ","thag19.1:39.2":"Muhum muhum caranikamva dassayam; ","thag19.1:39.3":"Ummattakeneva maya palobhasi, ","thag19.1:39.4":"Kincapi te citta viradhitam maya. ","thag19.1:40.1":"Idam pure cittamacari carikam, ","thag19.1:40.2":"Yenicchakam yatthakamam yathasukham; ","thag19.1:40.3":"Tadajjaham niggahessami yoniso, ","thag19.1:40.4":"Hatthippabhinnam viya ankusaggaho. ","thag19.1:41.1":"Sattha ca me lokamimam adhitthahi, ","thag19.1:41.2":"Aniccato addhuvato asarato; ","thag19.1:41.3":"Pakkhanda mam citta jinassa sasane, ","thag19.1:41.4":"Tarehi ogha mahata suduttara. ","thag19.1:42.1":"Na te idam citta yatha puranakam, ","thag19.1:42.2":"Naham alam tuyha vase nivattitum; ","thag19.1:42.3":"Mahesino pabbajitomhi sasane, ","thag19.1:42.4":"Na madisa honti vinasadharino. ","thag19.1:43.1":"Naga samudda sarita vasundhara, ","thag19.1:43.2":"Disa catasso vidisa adho diva; ","thag19.1:43.3":"Sabbe anicca tibhava upadduta, ","thag19.1:43.4":"Kuhim gato citta sukham ramissasi. ","thag19.1:44.1":"Dhitipparam kim mama citta kahisi, ","thag19.1:44.2":"Na te alam citta vasanuvattako; ","thag19.1:44.3":"Na jatu bhastam ubhatomukham chupe, ","thag19.1:44.4":"Dhiratthu puram nava sotasandanim. ","thag19.1:45.1":"Varahaeneyyavigalhasevite, ","thag19.1:45.2":"Pabbharakutte pakateva sundare; ","thag19.1:45.3":"Navambuna pavusasitthakanane, ","thag19.1:45.4":"Tahim guhagehagato ramissasi. ","thag19.1:46.1":"Sunilagiva susikha supekhuna, ","thag19.1:46.2":"Sucittapattacchadana vihangama; ","thag19.1:46.3":"Sumanjughosatthanitabhigajjino, ","thag19.1:46.4":"Te tam ramessanti vanamhi jhayinam. ","thag19.1:47.1":"Vutthamhi deve caturangule tine, ","thag19.1:47.2":"Sampupphite meghanibhamhi kanane; ","thag19.1:47.3":"Nagantare vitapisamo sayissam, ","thag19.1:47.4":"Tam me mudu hehiti tulasannibham. ","thag19.1:48.1":"Tatha tu kassami yathapi issaro, ","thag19.1:48.2":"Yam labbhati tenapi hotu me alam; ","thag19.1:48.3":"Na taham kassami yatha atandito, ","thag19.1:48.4":"Bilarabhastamva yatha sumadditam. ","thag19.1:49.1":"Tatha tu kassami yathapi issaro, ","thag19.1:49.2":"Yam labbhati tenapi hotu me alam; ","thag19.1:49.3":"Viriyena tam mayha vasanayissam, ","thag19.1:49.4":"Gajamva mattam kusalankusaggaho. ","thag19.1:50.1":"Taya sudantena avatthitena hi, ","thag19.1:50.2":"Hayena yoggacariyova ujjuna; ","thag19.1:50.3":"Pahomi maggam patipajjitum sivam, ","thag19.1:50.4":"Cittanurakkhihi sada nisevitam. ","thag19.1:51.1":"Arammane tam balasa nibandhisam, ","thag19.1:51.2":"Nagamva thambhamhi dalhaya rajjuya; ","thag19.1:51.3":"Tam me suguttam satiya subhavitam, ","thag19.1:51.4":"Anissitam sabbabhavesu hehisi. ","thag19.1:52.1":"Pannaya chetva vipathanusarinam, ","thag19.1:52.2":"Yogena niggayha pathe nivesiya; ","thag19.1:52.3":"Disva samudayam vibhavanca sambhavam, ","thag19.1:52.4":"Dayadako hehisi aggavadino. ","thag19.1:53.1":"Catubbipallasavasam adhitthitam, ","thag19.1:53.2":"Gamandalamva parinesi citta mam; ","thag19.1:53.3":"Nanu samyojanabandhanacchidam, ","thag19.1:53.4":"Samsevase karunikam mahamunim. ","thag19.1:54.1":"Migo yatha seri sucittakanane, ","thag19.1:54.2":"Rammam girim pavusaabbhamalinim; ","thag19.1:54.3":"Anakule tattha nage ramissam, ","thag19.1:54.4":"Asamsayam citta para bhavissasi. ","thag19.1:55.1":"Ye tuyha chandena vasena vattino, ","thag19.1:55.2":"Nara ca nari ca anubhonti yam sukham; ","thag19.1:55.3":"Aviddasu maravasanuvattino, ","thag19.1:55.4":"Bhavabhinandi tava citta savaka”ti. ","thag19.1:55.5":"… Talaputo thero … ","thag19.1:55.6":"Pannasanipato nitthito. ","thag19.1:56.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag19.1:56.1":"Pannasamhi nipatamhi, ","thag19.1:56.2":"eko talaputo suci; ","thag19.1:56.3":"Gathayo tattha pannasa, ","thag19.1:56.4":"puna panca ca uttariti. "}